       01  WS-WORKING-STORAGE.
           05  WS-SUB                       PIC S9(04) VALUE ZERO COMP.
           05  WS-MAX-BROWSE-LINES          PIC S9(04) VALUE +10  COMP.
           05  WS-BUS-FCN-ID                PIC X(04).
               88  WS-BUS-FCN-ID-VALID      VALUE '1940' '1941' '1942'
                                                  '1943' '1944'.
               88  WS-BUS-FCN-RETRIEVE      VALUE '1940'.
               88  WS-BUS-FCN-CREATE        VALUE '1941'.
               88  WS-BUS-FCN-UPDATE        VALUE '1942'.
               88  WS-BUS-FCN-DELETE        VALUE '1943'.
               88  WS-BUS-FCN-LIST          VALUE '1944'.
           05  WS-SECURITY-CLASS-LEVEL-IND  PIC X(01).
54-001         88  WS-SECURITY-CLASS-LEVEL-VALID VALUES '1' THRU '9'.
           05  WS-CONFIDENTIAL-ACCESS-IND   PIC X(01).
               88  WS-CONFIDENTIAL-ACCESS-VALID  VALUES 'B' 'C' 'N' 'P'.
