554712*-------------------------
554712*
554712*    IF  MIR-ETBL-DESC-TXT = EBLCH-BLANK-FIELD-CHAR
554712*        MOVE SPACES          TO MIR-ETBL-DESC-TXT
554712*    END-IF.
554712*
