      *-----------------------
012624*2335-EDIT-APPL-DEFN.
012624 2335-EDIT-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT.
      *-----------------------
      *
012624*    IF  MIR-SECUR-APPL-USE-TXT = EBLCH-BLANK-FIELD-CHAR
012624     IF  MIR-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT = EBLCH-BLANK-FIELD-CHAR
012624         MOVE ZEROS             TO MIR-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT
012624*        MOVE SPACES            TO MIR-SECUR-APPL-USE-TXT
012624     END-IF.

557659*    MOVE MIR-SECUR-APPL-USE-TXT      TO RUSCL-SECUR-APPL-DEFN-CD.
012624*    MOVE MIR-SECUR-APPL-USE-TXT      TO RUSCL-SECUR-APPL-USE-TXT.

012624     MOVE 'N'                         TO  L0280-SIGN-IND.
012624     MOVE 2                           TO  L0280-PRECISION.
012624     MOVE LENGTH OF MIR-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT TO L0280-INPUT-SIZE.
012624     COMPUTE L0280-LENGTH = L0280-INPUT-SIZE - 3.
012624     MOVE MIR-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT      TO L0280-INPUT-DATA.
012624     PERFORM  0280-1000-NUMERIC-EDIT
012624         THRU 0280-1000-NUMERIC-EDIT-X.

012624     IF L0280-OK
012624        MOVE L0280-OUTPUT-DOLLAR       TO RUSCL-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT
012624         PERFORM  0290-1000-BUILD-PARM-INFO
012624             THRU 0290-1000-BUILD-PARM-INFO-X
012624        COMPUTE L0290-INPUT-NUMBER = RUSCL-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT
012624                                   * 100
012624        MOVE +2                TO L0290-PRECISION
012624        MOVE LENGTH OF MIR-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT
012624                               TO L0290-MAX-OUT-LEN
012624        PERFORM  0290-1000-NUMERIC-FORMAT
012624            THRU 0290-1000-NUMERIC-FORMAT-X
012624        MOVE L0290-OUTPUT-DATA TO MIR-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT
012624     ELSE
012624*MSG : THE UNDERWRITING MAXIMUM SHOULD BE NUMERIC
012624        MOVE 'XS01600006'             TO  WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
012624        PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
012624            THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
012624     END-IF.

012624*2335-EDIT-APPL-DEFN-X.
012624 2335-EDIT-SECUR-CLAS-UWG-AMT-X.
           EXIT.
      /
